what is docker compose?
- The docker compose is a tool to manage the multi-containers as a single service.
How to create a docker compose file ?
- it is in the yaml format which understand by the humans
To run the docker-compose file 
- 'docker-compose up'
to remove all the containers
- 'docker-compose down'
- docker-compose build
- docker-compose logs
- docker-compose ps
- docker-compose version
- docker-compose port
- docker-compose top
- docker-compose kill
- docker-compose pause
- docker-compose unpause
- docker-compose rm
- docker-compose exec
- docker-compose run
- docker-compose pull